Changes in django-vcs-watch
===========================

0.2.3
-----

* Added option VCS_POSTPROCESS_COMMIT, which is a hook to manipulate with a
commit after it was fetched from a repository, but before it is saved to the
database.

0.2.2
-----

* Translation fix. Now locale is in the python package.

0.2.1
-----

* Russian translation was updated.

0.2.0
-----

* This version uses MongoDB to store diffs and all meta data.

0.1.4
-----

* Job was moved to 'hourly'.

0.1.3
-----

* Added flag 'zip_safe = False' to allow django-extensions discover jobs.

0.1.2
-----

* Fixed setup.py.

0.1.1

* First public release.
